4. Results
4.1. Validation of AI focus variable
Before conducting the main empirical analysis, we validated the construction of the AI focus variable. Prior studies suggest that
effective AI adoption typically requires substantial investment in data infrastructure and model development, including complementary
adjustments in organizational capabilities and business processes(Cockburn et al., 2019; Wamba-Taguimdje et al., 2020).
These studies emphasize that AI initiatives are generally accompanied by increased spending on R&D and SG&A functions(Mishra
